    <body>Click the down arrow to open a small window. In this window, you can enter the width of the border in the lower-left field. You can select the unit of measurement (e.g., pixels, points, centimeters) using the lower-left drop-down arrow. <MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="General.OnlineLive">See <MadCap:xref href="../../../Styles/More_About_Styles_and_Style_Sheets/About_Units_of_Measurement.htm">About Units of Measurement</MadCap:xref>. </MadCap:conditionalText>You can select a color for the border using the upper-right drop-down arrow. And you can select the type of line for the border (e.g., solid, dashed, dotted) using the lower-right drop-down arrow.</body>
</html>